tifically credible\\n\\n💡 Key Psychological Triggers:\\n- Creates a sense of urgency\\n- Offers an opportunity to be part of something bigger\\n- Makes space exploration feel personal and accessible\\n\\nThe section is designed to be the final push that converts interested visitors into active participants in the space exploration movement.\\n\\nWould you like me to elaborate on any aspect of this section plan?\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":3250,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":483,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
