            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "size": 2019,
            "text": "{\"id\":\"msg_01BnJEJ46Nwe6wXxGmVSD9m2\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"model\":\"claude-3-5-haiku-20241022\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"I'll help plan the Footer section for the space exploration website. Based on the provided guidelines and requirements, here's a comprehensive plan:\\n\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"availableSections\\\": [\\n    \\\"Hero\\\",\\n    \\\"Features\\\", \\n    \\\"Benefits\\\", \\n    \\\"Testimonials\\\", \\n    \\\"SocialProof\\\", \\n    \\\"CTA\\\"\\n  ]\\n}\\n```\\n\\nDetailed Footer Section Plan:\\n\\n1. Layout Description:\\n- 3-column responsive layout\\n- Left column: Logo and brief brand statement\\n- Middle column: Site navigation links\\n- Right column: Social media and contact information\\n- Background color: Deep space navy blue\\n- Text color: Soft luminescent blue-white\\n\\n2. Content Strategy:\\nNavigation Menu:\\n- Home (/#hero)\\n- Features (/#features)\\n- Benefits (/#benefits)\\n- Testimonials (/#testimonials)\\n- Contact CTA (/#cta)\\n\\n3. Visual Styling:\\n- Typography: Clean, modern sans-serif\\n- Icons: Lucide space/astronomy related icons\\n- Subtle constellation-like connecting lines between elements\\n- Slight parallax/hover effects on interactive elements\\n\\n4. Responsiveness:\\n- Mobile: Collapse to single column\\n- Stackable navigation links\\n- Centered content on smaller screens\\n\\n5. Recommended Components:\\n- @/components/ui/navigation-menu.tsx\\n- @/components/ui/separator.tsx\\n- @/components/ui/button.tsx (for social media links)\\n\\n6. Additional Elements:\\n- Copyright notice\\n- Privacy policy link\\n- Social media icons (GitHub, Twitter, LinkedIn)\\n- Optional newsletter signup\\n\\nThe footer maintains the inspirational, scientifically credible tone of the space exploration theme while providing clear, functional navigation.\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":2724,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":401,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
