            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-3-5-haiku-latest\",\"temperature\":0,\"top_k\":-1,\"top_p\":-1,\"stream\":false,\"max_tokens\":2048,\"tools\":[{\"name\":\"extract\",\"description\":\"A function available to call.\",\"input_schema\":{\"type\":\"object\",\"properties\":{\"suggestedComponents\":{\"anyOf\":[{\"type\":\"array\",\"items\":{\"type\":\"string\"}},{\"type\":\"null\"}],\"description\":\"List of suggested Shadcn UI components for this section.\"},\"headline\":{\"type\":[\"string\",\"null\"],\"description\":\"The headline for the CTA section (e.g., 'Ready to Get Started?').\"},\"supportingText\":{\"type\":[\"string\",\"null\"],\"description\":\"Supporting text for the CTA section (e.g., 'Don't miss out on this opportunity!').\"},\"paragraphs\":{\"type\":[\"string\",\"null\"],\"description\":\"Paragraphs of text to be included in the section.\"},\"cta\":{\"type\":\"object\",\"properties\":{\"text\":{\"type\":\"string\",\"description\":\"The text for the primary CTA button (e.g., 'Start Your Free Trial').\"}},\"required\":[\"text\"],\"additionalProperties\":false},\"supportingVisualOrTrustSignal\":{\"type\":[\"string\",\"null\"]},\"componentType\":{\"type\":\"string\",\"const\":\"CTA\"}},\"required\":[\"suggestedComponents\",\"headline\",\"supportingText\",\"paragraphs\",\"cta\",\"supportingVisualOrTrustSignal\",\"componentType\"],\"additionalProperties\":false,\"$schema\":\"http://json-schema.org/draft-07/schema#\"}}],\"tool_choice\":{\"type\":\"tool\",\"name\":\"extract\"},\"thinking\":{\"type\":\"disabled\"},\"messages\":[{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":\"Help the user plan a section of their website.\"},{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":\"I'll help plan the CTA (Call-to-Action) section for the space exploration landing page based on the provided context and guidelines. I'll generate a comprehensive section plan that captures the inspirational and scientific spirit of space exploration.\\n\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"suggestedComponents\\\": [\\n    \\\"@/components/ui/button.tsx\\\",\\n    \\\"@/components/ui/card.tsx\\\"\\n  ],\\n  \\\"headline\\\": \\\"Begin Your Space Journey Now\\\",\\n  \\\"supportingText\\\": \\\"Space exploration is accelerating at an unprecedented pace. Don't miss your chance to be part of this historic moment as humanity becomes a spacefaring civilization.\\\",\\n  \\\"paragraphs\\\": null,\\n  \\\"cta\\\": {\\n    \\\"text\\\": \\\"Join the Space Exploration Movement\\\"\\n  },\\n  \\\"supportingVisualOrTrustSignal\\\": \\\"A subtle constellation-like graphic or a minimalist icon of a rocket/telescope to reinforce the space exploration theme\\\"\\n}\\n```\\n\\nLet me break down the rationale behind this section plan:\\n\\n🎯 Section Goal:\\nThe CTA section is designed to create a sense of urgency and motivate immediate action, positioning space exploration as an accessible and exciting opportunity.\\n\\n📝 Content Strategy:\\n- Headline: \\\"Begin Your Space Journey Now\\\" - Direct, action-oriented, and inspiring\\n- Supporting Text: Emphasizes the unprecedented pace of space exploration and the user's potential to be part of a historic moment\\n- CTA Button: \\\"Join the Space Exploration Movement\\\" - Clear, engaging, and community-oriented\\n\\n🎨 Visual Considerations:\\n- Suggested components (Button, Card) allow for a clean, modern design\\n- The supporting visual element (constellation/rocket icon) maintains the space theme\\n- Aligns with brand guidelines of being inspirational and scientifically credible\\n\\n💡 Key Psychological Triggers:\\n- Creates a sense of urgency\\n- Offers an opportunity to be part of something bigger\\n- Makes space exploration feel personal and accessible\\n\\nThe section is designed to be the final push that converts interested visitors into active participants in the space exploration movement.\\n\\nWould you like me to elaborate on any aspect of this section plan?\"}]}"
