            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-3-5-haiku-latest\",\"temperature\":0,\"top_k\":-1,\"top_p\":-1,\"stream\":false,\"max_tokens\":2048,\"tools\":[{\"name\":\"extract\",\"description\":\"A function available to call.\",\"input_schema\":{\"type\":\"object\",\"properties\":{\"suggestedComponents\":{\"anyOf\":[{\"type\":\"array\",\"items\":{\"type\":\"string\"}},{\"type\":\"null\"}],\"description\":\"List of suggested Shadcn UI components for this section.\"},\"headline\":{\"type\":\"string\",\"description\":\"The main headline text.\"},\"subheadline\":{\"type\":[\"string\",\"null\"],\"description\":\"Supporting text below the headline.\"},\"paragraphs\":{\"type\":[\"string\",\"null\"],\"description\":\"Paragraphs of text to be included in the section.\"},\"ctaText\":{\"type\":[\"string\",\"null\"],\"description\":\"Text for the call-to-action button.\"},\"visualConcept\":{\"type\":[\"string\",\"null\"],\"description\":\"Description of the desired primary visual (image/video).\"},\"layoutVariant\":{\"type\":\"string\",\"enum\":[\"text-left-image-right\",\"image-left-text-right\",\"centered-overlay\",\"split-vertical\"],\"description\":\"Suggests a basic layout structure\"},\"visualEmphasis\":{\"type\":\"string\",\"enum\":[\"image-focus\",\"headline-focus\",\"cta-focus\"],\"description\":\"Which element should draw the most attention?\"},\"trustSignals\":{\"anyOf\":[{\"type\":\"array\",\"items\":{\"type\":\"string\"}},{\"type\":\"null\"}],\"description\":\"List of trust signals (e.g., 'As seen on Forbes', '5-star rating').\"},\"componentType\":{\"type\":\"string\",\"const\":\"Hero\"}},\"required\":[\"suggestedComponents\",\"headline\",\"subheadline\",\"paragraphs\",\"ctaText\",\"visualConcept\",\"layoutVariant\",\"visualEmphasis\",\"trustSignals\",\"componentType\"],\"additionalProperties\":false,\"$schema\":\"http://json-schema.org/draft-07/schema#\"}}],\"tool_choice\":{\"type\":\"tool\",\"name\":\"extract\"},\"thinking\":{\"type\":\"disabled\"},\"messages\":[{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":\"Help the user plan a section of their website.\"},{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":\"I'll help plan the Hero section for the space exploration website, focusing on creating an inspiring and engaging first impression that captures the wonder of space.\\n\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"suggestedComponents\\\": [\\n    \\\"@/components/ui/button.tsx\\\",\\n    \\\"@/components/ui/aspect-ratio.tsx\\\"\\n  ],\\n  \\\"headline\\\": \\\"The Stars Are Calling. Will You Answer?\\\",\\n  \\\"subheadline\\\": \\\"Embark on a journey beyond our world, where every discovery brings us closer to understanding the infinite universe.\\\",\\n  \\\"paragraphs\\\": null,\\n  \\\"ctaText\\\": \\\"Explore the Cosmos\\\",\\n  \\\"visualConcept\\\": \\\"A breathtaking high-resolution image of a distant galaxy, with vibrant blues and purples, showcasing the depth and mystery of space. The image should have a slight parallax effect to create depth and movement.\\\",\\n  \\\"layoutVariant\\\": \\\"text-left-image-right\\\",\\n  \\\"visualEmphasis\\\": \\\"image-focus\\\",\\n  \\\"trustSignals\\\": [\\n    \\\"Backed by NASA Research\\\",\\n    \\\"Trusted by Leading Astronomers\\\"\\n  ]\\n}\\n```\\n\\nLet me break down the rationale behind this Hero section plan:\\n\\n1. **Headline & Subheadline**: \\n   - The headline \\\"The Stars Are Calling. Will You Answer?\\\" is provocative and invites personal engagement.\\n   - The subheadline adds depth, suggesting a journey of discovery and connection to the universe.\\n\\n2. **Visual Concept**:\\n   - A galaxy image captures the awe and wonder of space exploration.\\n   - The color palette of blues and purples aligns with the brand guidelines.\\n   - The suggested parallax effect adds a sense of depth and movement.\\n\\n3. **Layout**:\\n   - Text-left, image-right layout allows for clear reading while providing a stunning visual backdrop.\\n   - Image-focus emphasis draws the eye and creates immediate emotional impact.\\n\\n4. **Call to Action**:\\n   - \\\"Explore the Cosmos\\\" is action-oriented and aligns with the inspirational tone.\\n\\n5. **Trust Signals**:\\n   - NASA research and astronomer endorsement add scientific credibility.\\n\\n6. **Components**:\\n   - Button component for CTA\\n   - Aspect ratio component to ensure consistent image sizing\\n\\nThe section aims to immediately capture the visitor's imagination, making space exploration feel personal and accessible while maintaining scientific integrity.\"}]}"
