            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-3-5-haiku-latest\",\"temperature\":0,\"top_k\":-1,\"top_p\":-1,\"stream\":false,\"max_tokens\":2048,\"tools\":[{\"name\":\"extract\",\"description\":\"A function available to call.\",\"input_schema\":{\"type\":\"object\",\"properties\":{\"suggestedComponents\":{\"anyOf\":[{\"type\":\"array\",\"items\":{\"type\":\"string\"}},{\"type\":\"null\"}],\"description\":\"List of suggested Shadcn UI components for this section.\"},\"headline\":{\"type\":[\"string\",\"null\"],\"description\":\"The headline for the social proof section (e.g., 'Trusted By').\"},\"contentType\":{\"type\":\"string\",\"enum\":[\"Logos\",\"Stats\",\"Awards\",\"Mix\"],\"description\":\"The primary type of social proof displayed.\"},\"paragraphs\":{\"type\":[\"string\",\"null\"],\"description\":\"Paragraphs of text to be included in the section.\"},\"logos\":{\"anyOf\":[{\"type\":\"array\",\"items\":{\"type\":\"string\"}},{\"type\":\"null\"}],\"description\":\"List of company names or identifiers for logos.\"},\"stats\":{\"anyOf\":[{\"type\":\"array\",\"items\":{\"type\":\"object\",\"properties\":{\"value\":{\"type\":\"string\",\"description\":\"The statistic value (e.g., '10,000+', '98%').\"},\"label\":{\"type\":\"string\",\"description\":\"The label or context for the statistic (e.g., 'Active Users', 'Customer Satisfaction').\"}},\"required\":[\"value\",\"label\"],\"additionalProperties\":false}},{\"type\":\"null\"}],\"description\":\"List of key statistics.\"},\"awards\":{\"anyOf\":[{\"type\":\"array\",\"items\":{\"type\":\"string\"}},{\"type\":\"null\"}],\"description\":\"List of award names or badges.\"},\"componentType\":{\"type\":\"string\",\"const\":\"SocialProof\"}},\"required\":[\"suggestedComponents\",\"headline\",\"contentType\",\"paragraphs\",\"logos\",\"stats\",\"awards\",\"componentType\"],\"additionalProperties\":false,\"$schema\":\"http://json-schema.org/draft-07/schema#\"}}],\"tool_choice\":{\"type\":\"tool\",\"name\":\"extract\"},\"thinking\":{\"type\":\"disabled\"},\"messages\":[{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":\"Help the user plan a section of their website.\"},{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":\"I'll help plan the Social Proof section for the space exploration website based on the provided context. I'll generate a comprehensive section plan that aligns with the brand guidelines and section goals.\\n\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"suggestedComponents\\\": [\\n    \\\"@/components/ui/card.tsx\\\",\\n    \\\"@/components/ui/tooltip.tsx\\\"\\n  ],\\n  \\\"headline\\\": \\\"Partners in Excellence\\\",\\n  \\\"contentType\\\": \\\"Logos\\\",\\n  \\\"paragraphs\\\": \\\"Our groundbreaking space exploration initiatives are powered by collaborations with the world's most innovative space organizations.\\\",\\n  \\\"logos\\\": [\\n    \\\"NASA Space Apps Challenge\\\",\\n    \\\"European Space Agency\\\", \\n    \\\"SpaceX Collaborative Research Initiative\\\"\\n  ],\\n  \\\"stats\\\": [\\n    {\\n      \\\"value\\\": \\\"3+\\\",\\n      \\\"label\\\": \\\"Major Space Research Partnerships\\\"\\n    },\\n    {\\n      \\\"value\\\": \\\"Global\\\",\\n      \\\"label\\\": \\\"Collaborative Network\\\"\\n    }\\n  ],\\n  \\\"awards\\\": null\\n}\\n```\\n\\nLet me break down the detailed plan for this Social Proof section:\\n\\n🎯 Section Goal:\\nThe section aims to establish credibility by showcasing strategic partnerships with renowned space organizations. It will build trust and demonstrate the project's scientific legitimacy.\\n\\n📐 Layout Design:\\n- Horizontal layout with logos arranged in a clean, modern grid\\n- Subtle background with deep space-inspired accent color\\n- Responsive design that collapses to a vertical stack on mobile\\n- Logos will have consistent sizing and subtle hover effects\\n\\n🎨 Visual Styling:\\n- Use bioluminescent blues and deep space purples\\n- Soft, subtle parallax effect to create depth\\n- Constellation-like connecting lines between logos\\n- Clean, modern typography with scientific precision\\n\\n💡 Key Design Considerations:\\n- Logos should be high-contrast against the background\\n- Use tooltips to provide additional context about each partnership\\n- Implement subtle animations to make the section feel dynamic\\n\\n🔍 Responsiveness:\\n- Mobile: Vertical logo stack\\n- Tablet: 2-column grid\\n- Desktop: 3-column grid with slight spacing between logos\\n\\nThe section leverages the brand's inspirational tone while maintaining scientific credibility, using the partners as social proof of the project's excellence.\\n\\nWould you like me to elaborate on any aspect of this section plan?\"}]}"
          },
