            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-3-5-haiku-latest\",\"temperature\":0,\"top_k\":-1,\"top_p\":-1,\"stream\":false,\"max_tokens\":2048,\"tools\":[{\"name\":\"extract\",\"description\":\"A function available to call.\",\"input_schema\":{\"type\":\"object\",\"properties\":{\"availableSections\":{\"type\":\"array\",\"items\":{\"type\":\"string\"},\"description\":\"List of available sections for the footer.\"},\"componentType\":{\"type\":\"string\",\"const\":\"Footer\"}},\"required\":[\"availableSections\",\"componentType\"],\"additionalProperties\":false,\"$schema\":\"http://json-schema.org/draft-07/schema#\"}}],\"tool_choice\":{\"type\":\"tool\",\"name\":\"extract\"},\"thinking\":{\"type\":\"disabled\"},\"messages\":[{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":\"Help the user plan a section of their website.\"},{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":\"I'll help plan the Footer section for the space exploration landing page. Based on the provided guidelines and requirements, here's a comprehensive plan:\\n\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"availableSections\\\": [\\n    \\\"Hero\\\",\\n    \\\"Features\\\", \\n    \\\"Benefits\\\", \\n    \\\"SocialProof\\\", \\n    \\\"Testimonials\\\", \\n    \\\"CTA\\\"\\n  ]\\n}\\n```\\n\\nDetailed Footer Section Plan:\\n\\n1. Layout Description:\\n- 3-column footer design\\n- Left column: Company/Brand information\\n- Middle column: Site Navigation\\n- Right column: Contact and Social Media links\\n- Dark background matching the cosmic theme (deep navy or space black)\\n- Subtle star-like particle effects as background accent\\n\\n2. Content Strategy:\\n- Company Logo with tagline\\n- Navigation Links to key sections:\\n  * Home (Hero)\\n  * Features\\n  * Benefits\\n  * Testimonials\\n  * Call to Action\\n- Social Media Icons (GitHub, Twitter/X, LinkedIn)\\n- Copyright notice\\n- Optional: Newsletter signup\\n\\n3. Visual Styling:\\n- Typography: Clean, modern sans-serif font\\n- Text Color: Soft white or light blue for readability\\n- Icons: Lucide space/astronomy related icons\\n- Hover effects with subtle glowing/pulsing animations\\n\\n4. Responsiveness:\\n- Mobile: Collapse to single column\\n- Stacked vertical layout on smaller screens\\n- Ensure touch-friendly icon sizes\\n- Responsive typography scaling\\n\\n5. Recommended Shadcn Components:\\n- @/components/ui/navigation-menu.tsx (for site links)\\n- @/components/ui/button.tsx (for social media links)\\n- @/components/ui/separator.tsx (for visual dividers)\\n\\n6. Interaction Notes:\\n- Smooth scroll to section links\\n- Hover states on navigation items\\n- External links open in new tabs\\n- Subtle hover animations to maintain cosmic theme\\n\\nThe footer will serve as a comprehensive navigation and information hub, maintaining the inspiring and scientific tone of the space exploration landing page.\"}]}"
