            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-3-5-haiku-latest\",\"temperature\":0,\"top_k\":-1,\"top_p\":-1,\"stream\":false,\"max_tokens\":2048,\"tools\":[{\"name\":\"extract\",\"description\":\"A function available to call.\",\"input_schema\":{\"type\":\"object\",\"properties\":{\"suggestedComponents\":{\"anyOf\":[{\"type\":\"array\",\"items\":{\"type\":\"string\"}},{\"type\":\"null\"}],\"description\":\"List of suggested Shadcn UI components for this section.\"},\"headline\":{\"type\":[\"string\",\"null\"],\"description\":\"The headline for the CTA section (e.g., 'Ready to Get Started?').\"},\"supportingText\":{\"type\":[\"string\",\"null\"],\"description\":\"Supporting text for the CTA section (e.g., 'Don't miss out on this opportunity!').\"},\"paragraphs\":{\"type\":[\"string\",\"null\"],\"description\":\"Paragraphs of text to be included in the section.\"},\"cta\":{\"type\":\"object\",\"properties\":{\"text\":{\"type\":\"string\",\"description\":\"The text for the primary CTA button (e.g., 'Start Your Free Trial').\"}},\"required\":[\"text\"],\"additionalProperties\":false},\"supportingVisualOrTrustSignal\":{\"type\":[\"string\",\"null\"]},\"componentType\":{\"type\":\"string\",\"const\":\"CTA\"}},\"required\":[\"suggestedComponents\",\"headline\",\"supportingText\",\"paragraphs\",\"cta\",\"supportingVisualOrTrustSignal\",\"componentType\"],\"additionalProperties\":false,\"$schema\":\"http://json-schema.org/draft-07/schema#\"}}],\"tool_choice\":{\"type\":\"tool\",\"name\":\"extract\"},\"thinking\":{\"type\":\"disabled\"},\"messages\":[{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":\"Help the user plan a section of their website.\"},{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":\"I'll help plan the CTA (Call-to-Action) section for the space exploration landing page based on the provided context and guidelines. I'll generate a comprehensive plan that captures the inspiring and awe-inducing tone of space exploration.\\n\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"suggestedComponents\\\": [\\n    \\\"@/components/ui/button.tsx\\\",\\n    \\\"@/components/ui/card.tsx\\\"\\n  ],\\n  \\\"headline\\\": \\\"Begin Your Space Journey\\\",\\n  \\\"supportingText\\\": \\\"Space exploration is accelerating at an unprecedented pace. Don't watch from the sidelines as humanity takes its next giant leap.\\\",\\n  \\\"paragraphs\\\": \\\"Join the movement that's shaping our species' future among the stars. Every great adventure starts with a single step - and your journey into the cosmos begins here.\\\",\\n  \\\"cta\\\": {\\n    \\\"text\\\": \\\"Join the Space Exploration Movement\\\"\\n  },\\n  \\\"supportingVisualOrTrustSignal\\\": \\\"A subtle background of twinkling stars or a minimalist cosmic gradient to reinforce the space theme\\\"\\n}\\n```\\n\\nLet me break down the rationale behind this section plan:\\n\\n1. **Headline & Supporting Text**: \\n   - Directly uses the provided copy, which captures the excitement and urgency of space exploration\\n   - Creates a sense of movement and personal invitation\\n\\n2. **Paragraphs**: \\n   - Expands on the original copy with an inspirational call to action\\n   - Emphasizes personal involvement and the transformative nature of space exploration\\n\\n3. **CTA Button**: \\n   - Provides a clear, action-oriented button text that invites participation\\n   - Aligns with the section's goal of motivating visitors to engage\\n\\n4. **Visual Approach**:\\n   - Suggested components (Button and Card) allow for a clean, modern design\\n   - The supporting visual hint maintains the cosmic theme from the brand guidelines\\n   - Keeps the focus on the call-to-action while providing a subtle space-themed context\\n\\n5. **Tone and Mood**:\\n   - Maintains the inspiring and awe-inducing tone specified in the brand guidelines\\n   - Evokes the feeling of looking through a telescope at a newly discovered galaxy\\n\\nThe section is designed to be the final push that converts interested visitors into active participants in the space exploration narrative, creating a sense of urgency and personal invitation to be part of something greater.\"}]}"
          },
