            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-3-5-haiku-latest\",\"temperature\":0,\"top_k\":-1,\"top_p\":-1,\"stream\":false,\"max_tokens\":2048,\"tools\":[{\"name\":\"extract\",\"description\":\"A function available to call.\",\"input_schema\":{\"type\":\"object\",\"properties\":{\"suggestedComponents\":{\"anyOf\":[{\"type\":\"array\",\"items\":{\"type\":\"string\"}},{\"type\":\"null\"}],\"description\":\"List of suggested Shadcn UI components for this section.\"},\"headline\":{\"type\":\"string\",\"description\":\"The main headline text.\"},\"subheadline\":{\"type\":[\"string\",\"null\"],\"description\":\"Supporting text below the headline.\"},\"paragraphs\":{\"type\":[\"string\",\"null\"],\"description\":\"Paragraphs of text to be included in the section.\"},\"ctaText\":{\"type\":[\"string\",\"null\"],\"description\":\"Text for the call-to-action button.\"},\"visualConcept\":{\"type\":[\"string\",\"null\"],\"description\":\"Description of the desired primary visual (image/video).\"},\"layoutVariant\":{\"type\":\"string\",\"enum\":[\"text-left-image-right\",\"image-left-text-right\",\"centered-overlay\",\"split-vertical\"],\"description\":\"Suggests a basic layout structure\"},\"visualEmphasis\":{\"type\":\"string\",\"enum\":[\"image-focus\",\"headline-focus\",\"cta-focus\"],\"description\":\"Which element should draw the most attention?\"},\"trustSignals\":{\"anyOf\":[{\"type\":\"array\",\"items\":{\"type\":\"string\"}},{\"type\":\"null\"}],\"description\":\"List of trust signals (e.g., 'As seen on Forbes', '5-star rating').\"},\"componentType\":{\"type\":\"string\",\"const\":\"Hero\"}},\"required\":[\"suggestedComponents\",\"headline\",\"subheadline\",\"paragraphs\",\"ctaText\",\"visualConcept\",\"layoutVariant\",\"visualEmphasis\",\"trustSignals\",\"componentType\"],\"additionalProperties\":false,\"$schema\":\"http://json-schema.org/draft-07/schema#\"}}],\"tool_choice\":{\"type\":\"tool\",\"name\":\"extract\"},\"thinking\":{\"type\":\"disabled\"},\"messages\":[{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":\"Help the user plan a section of their website.\"},{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":\"I'll help plan the Hero section for the space exploration website, focusing on creating an inspiring and engaging first impression that captures the wonder of space exploration.\\n\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"suggestedComponents\\\": [\\n    \\\"@/components/ui/button.tsx\\\",\\n    \\\"@/components/ui/aspect-ratio.tsx\\\"\\n  ],\\n  \\\"headline\\\": \\\"The Final Frontier Is Calling. Will You Answer?\\\",\\n  \\\"subheadline\\\": \\\"Embark on a journey beyond our world, where human curiosity meets cosmic exploration\\\",\\n  \\\"paragraphs\\\": \\\"Discover the boundless possibilities of space travel, scientific discovery, and humanity's next great adventure. From distant galaxies to unexplored planets, your exploration starts here.\\\",\\n  \\\"ctaText\\\": \\\"Begin Your Cosmic Journey\\\",\\n  \\\"visualConcept\\\": \\\"A breathtaking, high-resolution image of a spacecraft against a backdrop of stars and a distant nebula, with subtle particle animations suggesting movement and possibility\\\",\\n  \\\"layoutVariant\\\": \\\"text-left-image-right\\\",\\n  \\\"visualEmphasis\\\": \\\"image-focus\\\",\\n  \\\"trustSignals\\\": [\\n    \\\"Endorsed by NASA Researchers\\\",\\n    \\\"Featured in Scientific American\\\",\\n    \\\"5+ Years of Space Exploration Insights\\\"\\n  ]\\n}\\n```\\n\\nLet me break down the key elements of this Hero section plan:\\n\\n1. Headline Strategy:\\n   - The headline \\\"The Final Frontier Is Calling. Will You Answer?\\\" is provocative and invites personal engagement\\n   - It speaks directly to the human spirit of adventure and exploration\\n\\n2. Visual Concept:\\n   - The image description aligns with the brand's cosmic, awe-inspiring theme\\n   - Suggests movement and possibility through subtle animations\\n   - Positioned on the right side of the layout to create visual interest\\n\\n3. Layout and Emphasis:\\n   - Text-left, image-right layout allows for easy reading\\n   - Image-focus visual emphasis draws the eye and creates immediate emotional connection\\n\\n4. Call to Action:\\n   - \\\"Begin Your Cosmic Journey\\\" is action-oriented and matches the inspirational tone\\n   - Encourages immediate engagement\\n\\n5. Trust Signals:\\n   - Scientific credibility reinforced by mentions of NASA and Scientific American\\n   - Suggests expertise and reliability in space exploration content\\n\\nThe section is designed to immediately capture attention, communicate the core value of space exploration, and inspire visitors to learn more about the cosmic journey ahead.\"}]}"
          },
