          "postData": {
            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "params": [],
            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-3-5-haiku-latest\",\"temperature\":0,\"top_k\":-1,\"top_p\":-1,\"stream\":false,\"max_tokens\":2048,\"tools\":[{\"name\":\"extract\",\"description\":\"A function available to call.\",\"input_schema\":{\"type\":\"object\",\"properties\":{\"suggestedComponents\":{\"anyOf\":[{\"type\":\"array\",\"items\":{\"type\":\"string\"}},{\"type\":\"null\"}],\"description\":\"List of suggested Shadcn UI components for this section.\"},\"headline\":{\"type\":[\"string\",\"null\"],\"description\":\"The headline for the features section (e.g., 'Explore Key Features').\"},\"subheadline\":{\"type\":[\"string\",\"null\"],\"description\":\"Supporting text below the headline.\"},\"paragraphs\":{\"type\":[\"string\",\"null\"],\"description\":\"Paragraphs of text to be included in the section.\"},\"features\":{\"type\":\"array\",\"items\":{\"type\":\"object\",\"properties\":{\"name\":{\"type\":\"string\",\"description\":\"The name of the feature.\"},\"description\":{\"type\":\"string\",\"description\":\"A brief description of the feature.\"},\"visual\":{\"type\":[\"string\",\"null\"],\"description\":\"Description of the desired primary visual (image/video).\"}},\"required\":[\"name\",\"description\",\"visual\"],\"additionalProperties\":false}},\"cta\":{\"type\":[\"string\",\"null\"],\"description\":\"Text for a call-to-action button, if desired.\"},\"componentType\":{\"type\":\"string\",\"const\":\"Features\"}},\"required\":[\"suggestedComponents\",\"headline\",\"subheadline\",\"paragraphs\",\"features\",\"cta\",\"componentType\"],\"additionalProperties\":false,\"$schema\":\"http://json-schema.org/draft-07/schema#\"}}],\"tool_choice\":{\"type\":\"tool\",\"name\":\"extract\"},\"thinking\":{\"type\":\"disabled\"},\"messages\":[{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":\"Help the user plan a section of their website.\"},{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":\"I'll help plan the Features section for the space exploration landing page, focusing on creating an inspiring and informative overview of space exploration's accessibility.\\n\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"suggestedComponents\\\": [\\n    \\\"@/components/ui/card.tsx\\\",\\n    \\\"@/components/ui/icons/telescope.tsx\\\",\\n    \\\"@/components/ui/icons/rocket.tsx\\\"\\n  ],\\n  \\\"headline\\\": \\\"Space Exploration: No Longer Just a Dream\\\",\\n  \\\"subheadline\\\": \\\"Discover How Modern Technology is Opening the Cosmos to Everyone\\\",\\n  \\\"paragraphs\\\": \\\"For millennia, humans have gazed at the stars and wondered what lies beyond. Today, space exploration isn't just the domain of government agencies - it's becoming accessible to dreamers, innovators, and pioneers like you.\\\",\\n  \\\"features\\\": [\\n    {\\n      \\\"name\\\": \\\"Private Space Travel\\\",\\n      \\\"description\\\": \\\"Commercial space flight is transforming from science fiction to reality. Companies like SpaceX and Blue Origin are making space more accessible than ever before, offering unprecedented opportunities for civilian space exploration.\\\",\\n      \\\"visual\\\": \\\"rocket icon from lucide-react\\\"\\n    },\\n    {\\n      \\\"name\\\": \\\"Citizen Science\\\",\\n      \\\"description\\\": \\\"Advanced technologies and online platforms now allow everyday people to contribute to real space research. From analyzing satellite data to participating in crowdsourced astronomical observations, anyone can be a space explorer.\\\",\\n      \\\"visual\\\": \\\"telescope icon from lucide-react\\\"\\n    },\\n    {\\n      \\\"name\\\": \\\"Advanced Observation Technologies\\\",\\n      \\\"description\\\": \\\"Cutting-edge telescopes and satellite networks are providing unprecedented views of the universe. High-resolution imaging and real-time data streaming bring cosmic discoveries directly to your fingertips.\\\",\\n      \\\"visual\\\": \\\"satellite icon from lucide-react\\\"\\n    }\\n  ],\\n  \\\"cta\\\": \\\"Start Your Space Journey\\\"\\n}\\n```\\n\\nKey Design Considerations:\\n1. Visual Theme: Cosmic, inspiring, with a sense of wonder\\n2. Layout: Card-based feature display with icons\\n3. Color Scheme: Deep blues and purples with bright accent colors\\n4. Tone: Scientifically authoritative yet accessible and exciting\\n\\nThe section aims to demystify space exploration, showing how it's no longer an exclusive domain but an emerging field anyone can engage with. The features highlight technological advances that are making space more accessible, inspiring potential enthusiasts and supporters.\\n\\nThe suggested Shadcn UI components (cards, icons) will help create a clean, modern interface that communicates the exciting potential of space exploration to a broad audience.\"}]}"
          },
          "queryString": [],
          "url": "https://api.anthropic.com/v1/messages"
        },
        "response": {
          "bodySize": 1983,
          "content": {
            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "size": 1983,
            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-3-5-haiku-20241022\",\"id\":\"msg_016oxtRGhXirGDCsnu2h18n4\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"id\":\"toolu_01MtQADKsYyTGKdBFXxP5KvQ\",\"name\":\"extract\",\"input\":{\"suggestedComponents\":[\"@/components/ui/card.tsx\",\"@/components/ui/icons/telescope.tsx\",\"@/components/ui/icons/rocket.tsx\"],\"headline\":\"Space Exploration: No Longer Just a Dream\",\"subheadline\":\"Discover How Modern Technology is Opening the Cosmos to Everyone\",\"paragraphs\":\"For millennia, humans have gazed at the stars and wondered what lies beyond. Today, space exploration isn't just the domain of government agencies - it's becoming accessible to dreamers, innovators, and pioneers like you.\",\"features\":[{\"name\":\"Private Space Travel\",\"description\":\"Commercial space flight is transforming from science fiction to reality. Companies like SpaceX and Blue Origin are making space more accessible than ever before, offering unprecedented opportunities for civilian space exploration.\",\"visual\":\"rocket icon from lucide-react\"},{\"name\":\"Citizen Science\",\"description\":\"Advanced technologies and online platforms now allow everyday people to contribute to real space research. From analyzing satellite data to participating in crowdsourced astronomical observations, anyone can be a space explorer.\",\"visual\":\"telescope icon from lucide-react\"},{\"name\":\"Advanced Observation Technologies\",\"description\":\"Cutting-edge telescopes and satellite networks are providing unprecedented views of the universe. High-resolution imaging and real-time data streaming bring cosmic discoveries directly to your fingertips.\",\"visual\":\"satellite icon from lucide-react\"}],\"cta\":\"Start Your Space Journey\",\"componentType\":\"Features\"}}],\"stop_reason\":\"tool_use\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":1355,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_cr