            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-3-5-haiku-latest\",\"temperature\":0,\"top_k\":-1,\"top_p\":-1,\"stream\":false,\"max_tokens\":2048,\"tools\":[{\"name\":\"extract\",\"description\":\"A function available to call.\",\"input_schema\":{\"type\":\"object\",\"properties\":{\"suggestedComponents\":{\"anyOf\":[{\"type\":\"array\",\"items\":{\"type\":\"string\"}},{\"type\":\"null\"}],\"description\":\"List of suggested Shadcn UI components for this section.\"},\"headline\":{\"type\":[\"string\",\"null\"],\"description\":\"The headline for the testimonials section (e.g., 'What Our Customers Say').\"},\"subheadline\":{\"type\":[\"string\",\"null\"],\"description\":\"Optional supporting text below the headline.\"},\"paragraphs\":{\"type\":[\"string\",\"null\"],\"description\":\"Paragraphs of text to be included in the section.\"},\"testimonials\":{\"type\":\"array\",\"items\":{\"type\":\"object\",\"properties\":{\"quote\":{\"type\":\"string\",\"description\":\"The customer's testimonial quote.\"},\"name\":{\"type\":\"string\",\"description\":\"The name of the person providing the testimonial.\"},\"title_company\":{\"type\":\"string\",\"description\":\"Job title and/or company for context.\"},\"location\":{\"type\":[\"string\",\"null\"],\"description\":\"Optional location (e.g., City, State).\"},\"starRating\":{\"type\":[\"number\",\"null\"],\"description\":\"Star rating if applicable (e.g., 4.5 stars).\"}},\"required\":[\"quote\",\"name\",\"title_company\",\"location\",\"starRating\"],\"additionalProperties\":false},\"description\":\"An array of testimonials.\"},\"componentType\":{\"type\":\"string\",\"const\":\"Testimonials\"}},\"required\":[\"suggestedComponents\",\"headline\",\"subheadline\",\"paragraphs\",\"testimonials\",\"componentType\"],\"additionalProperties\":false,\"$schema\":\"http://json-schema.org/draft-07/schema#\"}}],\"tool_choice\":{\"type\":\"tool\",\"name\":\"extract\"},\"thinking\":{\"type\":\"disabled\"},\"messages\":[{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":\"Help the user plan a section of their website.\"},{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":\"I'll help plan the Testimonials section for the space exploration website, following the detailed instructions and brand guidelines. I'll create a comprehensive section plan that captures the essence of inspiring space exploration stories.\\n\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"suggestedComponents\\\": [\\n    \\\"@/components/ui/card.tsx\\\",\\n    \\\"@/components/ui/avatar.tsx\\\"\\n  ],\\n  \\\"headline\\\": \\\"Voyagers of Vision: Real Stories of Cosmic Discovery\\\",\\n  \\\"subheadline\\\": \\\"Hear from innovators who transformed their space passion into groundbreaking achievements\\\",\\n  \\\"paragraphs\\\": \\\"At Stellar Horizons, we believe every space enthusiast has the potential to contribute to humanity's greatest adventure. Our community doesn't just dream about the stars—we help you reach them.\\\",\\n  \\\"testimonials\\\": [\\n    {\\n      \\\"quote\\\": \\\"Stellar Horizons connected me with mentors who helped me launch my space startup, turning my cosmic dreams into a tangible reality.\\\",\\n      \\\"name\\\": \\\"Sarah K.\\\",\\n      \\\"title_company\\\": \\\"Founder, AstraTech Innovations\\\",\\n      \\\"location\\\": \\\"San Francisco, CA\\\",\\n      \\\"starRating\\\": 5.0\\n    },\\n    {\\n      \\\"quote\\\": \\\"I went from being a space enthusiast to contributing to actual satellite projects. This platform transformed my passion into a professional journey.\\\",\\n      \\\"name\\\": \\\"Mark R.\\\",\\n      \\\"title_company\\\": \\\"Aerospace Engineer\\\",\\n      \\\"location\\\": \\\"Houston, TX\\\", \\n      \\\"starRating\\\": 4.5\\n    }\\n  ]\\n}\\n```\\n\\nLet me break down the key aspects of this section plan:\\n\\n🌟 Headline Strategy:\\n- Captures the inspirational tone of space exploration\\n- Emphasizes personal transformation and achievement\\n- Uses evocative language (\\\"Voyagers of Vision\\\")\\n\\n📝 Content Approach:\\n- Highlights real user experiences\\n- Demonstrates tangible outcomes of using the platform\\n- Provides context about how Stellar Horizons supports space enthusiasts\\n\\n🎨 Visual Considerations:\\n- Suggested using Card and Avatar components for a clean, professional look\\n- Implied cosmic/space theme through language and design\\n- Ratings and personal details add credibility\\n\\n💡 Key Differentiators:\\n- Specific quotes showing actual career/project progression\\n- Geographic diversity in testimonials\\n- High star ratings reinforcing platform's value\\n\\nThe plan follows the brand guidelines by maintaining an inspiring, scientifically authoritative tone while evoking the wonder of space exploration. The testimonials showcase how the platform transforms space enthusiasm into real-world achievements.\\n\\nWould you like me to elaborate on any part of the section plan?\"}]}"
          },
