            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-3-5-haiku-latest\",\"temperature\":0,\"top_k\":-1,\"top_p\":-1,\"stream\":false,\"max_tokens\":2048,\"tools\":[{\"name\":\"extract\",\"description\":\"A function available to call.\",\"input_schema\":{\"type\":\"object\",\"properties\":{\"suggestedComponents\":{\"anyOf\":[{\"type\":\"array\",\"items\":{\"type\":\"string\"}},{\"type\":\"null\"}],\"description\":\"List of suggested Shadcn UI components for this section.\"},\"headline\":{\"type\":[\"string\",\"null\"],\"description\":\"The headline for the social proof section (e.g., 'Trusted By').\"},\"contentType\":{\"type\":\"string\",\"enum\":[\"Logos\",\"Stats\",\"Awards\",\"Mix\"],\"description\":\"The primary type of social proof displayed.\"},\"paragraphs\":{\"type\":[\"string\",\"null\"],\"description\":\"Paragraphs of text to be included in the section.\"},\"logos\":{\"anyOf\":[{\"type\":\"array\",\"items\":{\"type\":\"string\"}},{\"type\":\"null\"}],\"description\":\"List of company names or identifiers for logos.\"},\"stats\":{\"anyOf\":[{\"type\":\"array\",\"items\":{\"type\":\"object\",\"properties\":{\"value\":{\"type\":\"string\",\"description\":\"The statistic value (e.g., '10,000+', '98%').\"},\"label\":{\"type\":\"string\",\"description\":\"The label or context for the statistic (e.g., 'Active Users', 'Customer Satisfaction').\"}},\"required\":[\"value\",\"label\"],\"additionalProperties\":false}},{\"type\":\"null\"}],\"description\":\"List of key statistics.\"},\"awards\":{\"anyOf\":[{\"type\":\"array\",\"items\":{\"type\":\"string\"}},{\"type\":\"null\"}],\"description\":\"List of award names or badges.\"},\"componentType\":{\"type\":\"string\",\"const\":\"SocialProof\"}},\"required\":[\"suggestedComponents\",\"headline\",\"contentType\",\"paragraphs\",\"logos\",\"stats\",\"awards\",\"componentType\"],\"additionalProperties\":false,\"$schema\":\"http://json-schema.org/draft-07/schema#\"}}],\"tool_choice\":{\"type\":\"tool\",\"name\":\"extract\"},\"thinking\":{\"type\":\"disabled\"},\"messages\":[{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":\"Help the user plan a section of their website.\"},{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":\"I'll help plan the Social Proof section for the space exploration landing page, focusing on building credibility and inspiring trust in the space exploration community.\\n\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"suggestedComponents\\\": [\\n    \\\"@/components/ui/card.tsx\\\",\\n    \\\"@/components/ui/avatar.tsx\\\",\\n    \\\"@/components/ui/badge.tsx\\\"\\n  ],\\n  \\\"headline\\\": \\\"Pioneers of the Cosmic Frontier\\\",\\n  \\\"contentType\\\": \\\"Mix\\\",\\n  \\\"paragraphs\\\": \\\"Our diverse community represents the cutting edge of space exploration, bringing together brilliant minds from around the globe to push the boundaries of human knowledge and technological innovation.\\\",\\n  \\\"logos\\\": [\\n    \\\"NASA\\\",\\n    \\\"SpaceX\\\", \\n    \\\"Blue Origin\\\",\\n    \\\"European Space Agency\\\"\\n  ],\\n  \\\"stats\\\": [\\n    {\\n      \\\"value\\\": \\\"500+\\\",\\n      \\\"label\\\": \\\"Space Professionals Involved\\\"\\n    },\\n    {\\n      \\\"value\\\": \\\"25\\\",\\n      \\\"label\\\": \\\"Active Research Projects\\\"\\n    },\\n    {\\n      \\\"value\\\": \\\"10\\\",\\n      \\\"label\\\": \\\"Countries Represented\\\"\\n    }\\n  ],\\n  \\\"awards\\\": [\\n    \\\"Innovative Space Technology Award\\\",\\n    \\\"Global Space Exploration Summit Recognition\\\"\\n  ]\\n}\\n```\\n\\nLet me break down the detailed plan for this Social Proof section:\\n\\n🎨 Visual Design Approach:\\n- Layout: Grid-based design with logos, stats, and brief community description\\n- Background: Deep space-inspired dark blue/purple gradient\\n- Typography: Clean, modern sans-serif fonts in contrasting light colors\\n- Emphasis on creating a sense of collective achievement and global collaboration\\n\\n📐 Layout Strategy:\\n- Top: Headline \\\"Pioneers of the Cosmic Frontier\\\"\\n- Middle: Logos of key space organizations in a horizontal grid\\n- Bottom: Key statistics showcasing community scale and impact\\n- Optional: Small section highlighting awards or recognition\\n\\n🌟 Key Design Considerations:\\n- Use subtle star-like particle animations in the background\\n- Ensure logos are high-contrast and easily recognizable\\n- Create a sense of scale and global reach\\n- Highlight the diversity and collaborative nature of space exploration\\n\\n📱 Responsiveness:\\n- Mobile: Collapse to vertical stack\\n- Logos will resize and potentially wrap\\n- Statistics will stack vertically\\n- Maintain readability and visual hierarchy\\n\\nThe section aims to build credibility by showcasing:\\n1. Recognized organizations (logos)\\n2. Scale of community involvement (stats)\\n3. Breadth of research and global representation\\n4. Professional recognition (awards)\\n\\nThis approach transforms the social proof from a simple logo display to a narrative about the exciting, collaborative world of space exploration.\"}]}"
